{"tid":735629,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"【遊台注意】超強颱風「瑪莉亞」迫台 下沉氣流襲港周三酷熱","createTime":"2018-07-09T15:33:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T04:08:30.000Z","uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ddcf61066f7aa783d11ff0c1065aa47f016fb6a5","tid":735629,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:33:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1624643/org/b0a7cce97aacc62f888226724770098e.jpg/DN0fN-6C63WAf7JLf-PrAe922TRMYG3kdnh5B3Z4eQc?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1624643%2Forg%2Fb0a7cce97aacc62f888226724770098e.jpg%2FDN0fN-6C63WAf7JLf-PrAe922TRMYG3kdnh5B3Z4eQc%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=cca1ea00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n超強颱風瑪莉亞集結在沖繩島之東南約1,360公里，預料向西北偏西移動，時速約20公里，移向台灣以北至琉球群島一帶。預料瑪莉亞外圍的下沉氣流會在本週中期為廣東沿岸帶來酷熱的天氣。<br />\n<br />\n而台灣中央氣象局預測，上午8時瑪莉亞維持強烈颱風強度，以每小時21公里速度，向西北西的台灣陸地進逼，強度逐漸增強，暴風圈由200公里擴大至250公里，預料今晚（8日）台灣各區普遍是多雲時晴，而明日（9日）各區則普遍多雲午後短暫雷陣雨。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180709/_2018070912063783850.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180709%2F_2018070912063783850.jpg&h=83ff0dd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天文台預測本港明日短暫時間有陽光，有幾陣驟雨，初時局部地區有雷暴，氣溫27至31度。周三部分時間有陽光及有煙霞，天氣酷熱，稍後局部地區有驟雨，氣溫28至33度。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://pda.hko.gov.hk/mtsate/MTSAT1RIR/mtsat_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpda.hko.gov.hk%2Fmtsate%2FMTSAT1RIR%2Fmtsat_2.jpg&h=3443bbda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n周五起有雷暴，當日大致多雲，有幾陣驟雨及雷暴。稍後驟雨增多，氣溫27至30度。周六起大致多雲，有驟雨及雷暴，氣溫跌至介乎26至29度。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/b/b6/Maria_2018-07-08_0630Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fb%2Fb6%2FMaria_2018-07-08_0630Z.png&h=082ecaa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n超強颱風瑪莉亞 Typhoon Maria <br />\n<br />\n十分鐘平均風速 <br />\n颱風 （JMA）\t195 km/h（105 kt）<br />\n強烈颱風 （CWB）\t200 km/h（55 m/s）<br />\n超強颱風 （KMA）\t180 km/h（50 m/s）<br />\n超強颱風 （HKO）\t220 km/h<br />\n颱風 （PAGASA）\t200 km/h<br />\n颱風 （TMD）\t195 km/h（105 kt）<br />\n<br />\n兩分鐘平均風速<br />\n超強颱風 （CMA）\t215 km/h（60 m/s）<br />\n<br />\n一分鐘平均風速<br />\n超級颱風 （JTWC）\t260 km/h（140 kt）<br />\n<br />\n最低氣壓\t915 hPa<br />\n瞬間最大陣風\t280 km/h"},{"pid":"d0fbcfb44c0f3a7f6e1497fe0642d23854cd7261","tid":735629,"uid":42629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T03:27:41.000Z","msg":"呢個風係咪勁？仲要吹正台灣"},{"pid":"d1501da7a227cb3717ada144037c0c27a2aa2fef","tid":735629,"uid":40817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T03:33:07.000Z","msg":"人在台北 暫時咩事都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91a1537685dbf502853caa85cd19413116ffbb00","tid":735629,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T04:03:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/10/120357_ad34357b771a4994a94339bcba4600d8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F10%2F120357_ad34357b771a4994a94339bcba4600d8.png&h=d57086f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8e9bec12fcc300f86d5ff8e435711a237e0a7e5","tid":735629,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T04:08:30.000Z","msg":"臺灣反而小事，香港飛臺北都唔係好多機停<br />\n<br />\n但沖繩真係今日全停。"}]}